- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses baseline models for addressing the different modalities. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is possible as the paper mentions the annotation process for the dataset. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also possible as the dataset could be used for video search and retrieval applications.
